\series default
.
 In this way the model is obviously preparation contextual since the distributio
n that represents a convex combination of preparation procedures 
\begin_inset Formula $\mu\left(\psi\right)=\int_{\Lambda}p\left(\psi'\right)\delta\left(\psi-\psi'\right)\,\mathrm{d}\psi'$
\end_inset

 depends on the particular ensemble of pure states and not just on the density
 operator associated with the mixture.
 
